wanna know what I love?

last year Phil would always take pictures and post pictures of Dan because he thought he was beautiful and he was so happy for him for embracing his hair and becoming more confident…

this year Phil is posting more of himself for the exact same reason.

okay first cornelia posts a boat pic of martyn to her instagram.
then dan posts a boat pic of phil to his instagram.
now...
body:
okay first cornelia posts a boat pic of martyn to her instagram.

then dan posts a boat pic of phil to his instagram.

now cornelia posts a picture of her and martyn trying to fit in the hobbit home.

and dan of course posts a picture of him and phil trying to fit in the hobbit home.

i’m sensing a pattern here…
